snippet.title: Ultimate League Season 2
snippet.description:
Football Superstars Ultimate League is back with Season 2. This season's line-up is Angels Sc, Arcadia Fc, Devils Fc, FC.Crvena Zvezda, Monte Fc, Newteam, Outlaws Sc, Razer Sc, Redwhite United, Serene, Vampire Sc and Vipers Sc. Good luck to all teams!

Join league and tournaments at http://www.superstarsleague.com
